org.apache.hadoop.fs.azure

Class SecureWasbRemoteCallHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.fs.azure.WasbRemoteCallHelper
      • org.apache.hadoop.fs.azure.SecureWasbRemoteCallHelper

  • public class SecureWasbRemoteCallHelper
extends WasbRemoteCallHelper
    Helper class the has constants and helper methods used in WASB when integrating with a remote http cred service which uses Kerberos and delegation tokens. Currently, remote service will be used to generate SAS keys, authorization and delegation token operations.
